      <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
         <head>Biographical History</head>
         
      <p> 	Bolta Products of Lawrence, Massachusetts, a division of General Tire &amp; Rubber Corporation, was a plastics manufacturer that produced a line of domestic tableware called Boltaware.</p>
</bioghist>
      
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
